Vallen Zek <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugrimmlokk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grimmlokk</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://grimmlokk.homestead.com/files/icon.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/2/02 2:12:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19.topic&index=42>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://grimmlokk.homestead.com/files/spinhead2.gif?flezbwidth=30&flezbheight=41? WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Silly tanks</span><hr size=1> Red Server - Hills guud. Use them. You are *fighting* not duelling. Winning is actually pretty important.<br>
